rComments: An okay professor. But like all management professors, keeping the class average in the C range was his goal. Gave an decent midterm, but CLOBBERED us on the final, which was not fair at all. The profs should have to create the midterm and final at the same time. It's not our fault the average is high. Why should we get penalized for studying?
